1.0.name: wordpress/modesty
1.0.description: In my opinion it is a simple and elegant theme which is designed to display content in a fast and good looking way. Like a blog should do it this theme shows its content in a well structured way. In this theme the sidebar is in the bottom and not on a side of the page.
